940
01:08:17,849 --> 01:08:24,850
And then I come to find out, and I think we should get to the bottom of this, because this is part of our budgetary process.

941
01:08:25,710 --> 01:08:32,152
I understand that Mr. Prior Principal of the school is up at the high school with another job getting paid the same amount of money.

942
01:08:33,004 --> 01:08:36,626
