948
01:09:20,833 --> 01:09:22,174
Yeah.

949
01:09:24,395 --> 01:09:27,036
On the motion of counselor Penta to ask the school committee, the superintendent,

950
01:09:27,810 --> 01:09:43,528
I would say it would be the superintendent, because he must have done the hiring, and it would be nice to know what's the job that he has up at the high school, what's that salary, and what's the job of the lady or the man who's now the principal of the Turtus Cuff, and what's that salary?

951
01:09:45,871 --> 01:09:47,012
It's a confusing little story.

952
01:09:48,682 --> 01:09:52,885
I think amazed at me that I didn't know because I just made an assumption that he was still there as the principal.

953
01:09:53,325 --> 01:09:55,026
